      "title": "Bandula becomes independent",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Bandula Gunawardena said that he will leave the position of Minister of Transport, Highways and Mass Media and the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna and work independently in Parliament.",
        "Mr. Gunawardena has taken this decision considering the current situation in the country."
      ],
